  id: FractionatedMorseCipher
  title: Fractionated Morse Cipher
  author: BCMGF1137
  description: 'Yes, I''m aware Indigo Cipher has a Fractionated Morse Cipher in it,
    but in this module, you''re decrypting sentences! Good luck...


    ///


    Determine the keyword used in a Fractionated Morse Cipher that encrypts a message
    from some module''s alternative manual.


    ///


    After my sister participated in a science olympiad (twice), I decided to make
    this module. I was originally going to use Discord messages, but I decided to
    switch to manuals since they are more recognizable. Having a sentence did lead
    to long ciphertexts (~100 characters), so I decided to assist with this step by
    adding the number of characters used.


    I guess have fun with figuring out some principles for this mod... and please
    don''t try to crack all the possible messages/keywords that can appear on this
    module.


    Oh yeah, and there''s Twitch Plays inside if you want.


    ///


    Song used: "VerTex^3"/"VVV" by ZiGZaG (yes, the song has two names)'
  version: 1
  outputFolder: build
  previewImage: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 08eba15e3cb28334996e10882aea123d, type: 3}
